reviewText: I have the whole collection I must say it's pretty good easy to learn and fallowing along.

before you go and say its fake...this guy has really been taught by jinichi kawakami!!! now its not clear if the rank he recieved was in the kurondo reenactors ninja group or the banke shinobiden art which is supposedly kkoga ryu...i liked it honestly the best stuff out there on koga ryu other than soke kawakami himself..
